  "description": "**Milestone:** Ava Home Screen\n\nModify src/cli/cmd/tui/routes/home.tsx to replace the session history list with a board status panel. Fetch board summary from Automaker API (localhost:3008/api/board/summary): total, backlog, in-progress, review, blocked counts. Display as a clean summary table. Show recent features (last 5 updated) below. Graceful fallback when Automaker is offline. Chat prompt remains at bottom and is focused by default.\n\n**Files to Modify:**\n- packages/opencode/src/cli/cmd/tui/routes/home.tsx\n\n**Acceptance Criteria:**\n- [ ] Home screen shows board summary when Automaker is running\n- [ ] Board counts are accurate\n- [ ] Graceful fallback when Automaker is offline\n- [ ] Chat prompt is accessible and focused by default\n- [ ] Refreshes on focus\n\n**Complexity:** large\n\n**Guardrails:** If this phase involves new or changed behavior, include tests that verify correctness. If this phase adds, removes, or changes a user-facing feature, API endpoint, configuration option, or service, update the relevant documentation in `docs/` to reflect those changes.",
